body:
I was playing Vel&#039;koz today in ranked, and I was about 4 kills and 60 CS up on Lux. Suddenly, she finishes a few items and THREE SHOTS ME. 
(Edit: didn't include boots initially, but they play a factor as well) 
(Edit 2: She had like no CS and no kills at 33 minutes. Where the fuck did she get so many more items? OP edited to be accurate.)

I had: {{item:3174}} {{item:3089}} {{item:1058}} {{item:3113}} {{item:3158}} 

She had: {{item:3165}} {{item:3157}} {{item:3089}} {{item:3020}} 






What the fuck.

replies.body:
